esfangbegrenzung:</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">2 Karpfen, 4 Schleien, 3 Aale, 2 Forellen, sonstige keine Begrenzung</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><b>Fangmaße und Schonzeiten:</b></p><ul type=\"disc\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; margin-top: 0cm;\"><li class=\"MsoNormal\">Karpfen: 35 cm // -&nbsp;</li><li class=\"MsoNormal\">Schleien: 30 cm // 01.05. - 30.06.</li><li class=\"MsoNormal\">Aale: 50 cm // 01.11. - 28.02.</li><li class=\"MsoNormal\">Forelle: 26 cm // 01.10. - 30.04.</li></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">Für Inhaber von Jugendkarten ist das Angeln nur mit&nbsp;<b>einer</b>&nbsp;Handangel erlaubt.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>","rules_files":[{"id":1441252,"name":"tageskarte-jugend-bestimmungen","description":null,"file":"https://api.hejfish.com/files/download/9f45f5ec8fa001222eca7fdc61cbbb18546b54b7/tageskarte-jugend-bestimmungen.pdf"}],"additional_areas":[],"catch_report_required":true}],"manager":{"id":1957,"name":"Fischereiverein Neumarkt e.V. ","street":"Max-Bögl-Straße 40","postal_code":"92369","city":"Sengenthal","telephone":"0171-5527534","email":"verwaltung@fv-nm.de","website":"https://fv-nm.de","logo":"https://file.hejfish.com/image/r200x200/19/f5/19f5715af115cf52bc8e84a2a14b5d980f37cc62.png","slug":"fischereiverein-neumarkt-e-v"},"season_begin":"0001-01-01","season_end":"0001-11-01","features":{"accessible":false,"public_transport":true,"boat":false,"belly_boat":false,"digital_ticket":false,"night_fishing":true,"ice_fishing":false,"depth_map":false,"has_gauges":tr